result.name: venture-data
result.notes: Information about each cohort of ventures which has been supported by the Social Incubator East.

organization.name: social-incubator-east
organization.title: Social Incubator East
organization.description:
The data shows incubator and venture level detail about the Social Incubator Fund, a £10m fund administered by BIG, which supports social incubators to help them provide investment and support to early stage social ventures in the UK. The data is available for all live incubators and is updated by the incubators themselves. This data has been submitted by Social Incubator East.

A data visualization platform of the Cabinet Office Investment Readiness Programme can be viewed here: http://data.gov.uk/data/viz/investment-readiness-programme

More details at http://www.socialincubatoreast.org.uk

result.title: Venture data - Social Incubator East
